init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So this alien brings him to a far away planet where he can live, for now.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Because of this, the aliens do not have to eat.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is bad news for Matt Damon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: If he does not eat, he will starve to death.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But the guard does not understand.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien does not understand why he would be pretending to chew on his arm.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They do not understand why humans would have evolved to have the need for them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He sees a tree through the window of his prison.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But the window is too high up for him to reach.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The guard asks him why he is crying.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He leads him to a field near the tree.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells Matt Damon to stand in the field.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After a few steps, he tells Matt Damon to run.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He thinks the guard is following him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He runs over a hill and begins to slide down the other side.
